    <h1>Freemium</h1>
    <p class="description">A business model where the core product is permanently free, with revenue from premium upgrades. Average conversion rate is <strong>2–5%</strong>. Used by Spotify, Dropbox, Slack, Canva, and Mailchimp.</p>
